<div dir="ltr">Ralph,<div><br></div><div>Does some part of the &quot;<span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px">timer that is firing to indicate a </span><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px">failed connection attempt&quot; theory explain the case of singletons hanging?  I&#39;m just bringing this up in case you might be looking in the wrong direction.</span></div>
